\\r\\nLe m\\u00e9dicament n\'a pas march\\u00e9 ?\\r\\nIl va y avoir du boulot pour refermer ce bazar ! \\u00bb<\\/p>\\r\\n                        \\r\\n                        <h2>Chapter 2: The Adventure<\\/h2>\\r\\n                        <p>One day, while exploring the enchanted forest, our hero made an amazing discovery...<\\/p>\\r\\n                        \\r\\n                        <h2>Chapter 3: The Lesson<\\/h2>\\r\\n                        <p>And so, after this wonderful adventure, everyone learned that the most important thing is to believe in yourself and never stop learning!<\\/p>","age_range":"3-13","reading_time":3,"thumbnail":"stories\\/wSrjPu0NpiiQVzoSM62NdD2xchCvMrp4N0T2RWLL.png","views":40,"rating":5,"rating_count":8,"is_published":true,"created_at":"2025-04-26T01:08:35.000000Z","updated_at":"2025-04-26T01:09:55.000000Z","audio_file":"stories\\/audio\\/PqtFEIUe7C7ZDDq8IAlFyiiTyiCCnAybRVK1XILz.mp3","audio_duration":null,"audio_url":null,"video_file":null,"video_duration":null,"video_url":null,"category":{"id":1,"name":"Albums et histoires","slug":"albums-et-histoires","description":"D\\u00e9couvrez des histoires magnifiquement illustr\\u00e9es","icon":null,"color":"#2563eb","order":1,"created_at":"2025-04-26T01:08:35.000000Z","updated_at":"2025-04-26T01:08:35.000000Z"}},{"id":2,"category_id":1,"title":"Story 2 in Albums et histoires","slug":"story-2-in-albums-et-histoires","description":"This is a sample story in the Albums et histoires category. It\'s perfect for kids who love reading!","content":"<h2>Chapter 1: The Beginning<\\/h2>\\r\\n                        <p>Once upon a time, in a magical world far away, there lived a curious child who loved to learn new things...<\\/p>\\r\\n                        \\r\\n                        <h2>Chapter 2: The Adventure<\\/h2>\\r\\n                        <p>One day, while exploring the enchanted forest, our hero made an amazing discovery...<\\/p>\\r\\n                        \\r\\n                    